<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She always shows off her sartorial prowess when she hits the town.</p>

<p>And Hailey Bieber looked sensational when she made her way to a meeting in Los Angeles, California, on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The model, 23, put on a very leggy display as she dressed up in an oversized black jacket and shorts for the appointment.</p>

