<p>Hailey boosted her height in a pair of heavy-duty black boots that accentuated her slender legs, while she finished off her look with a simple black top.</p>

<p>Her brunette locks were brushed into a sleek, straight style, and she used a light palette of make-up for the occasion. </p>

<p>The model kept safe amid the coronavirus crisis by wearing a black face mask, and she accessorised with an array of silver necklaces.</p>

